<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Compra Exitosa - NutriPills</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div
      class="fixed inset-0 z-50 grid place-content-center bg-black/50 p-4"
      role="dialog"
      aria-modal="true"
      aria-labelledby="modalTitle"
    >
      <div class="w-full max-w-md rounded-lg bg-white p-6 shadow-lg dark:bg-gray-900">
        <h2 id="modalTitle" class="text-xl font-bold text-center text-gray-900 sm:text-2xl dark:text-white">
          Compra Exitosa!
        </h2>

        <div class="mt-4 flex flex-col items-center gap-4">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="mx-auto h-16 w-16 text-green-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12l2 2l4 -4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0a9 9 0 0118 0z" />
        </svg>
          <p class="text-pretty text-center text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
            La compra ha sido realizada con éxito. <br>¡Gracias por elegir NutriPills para tu bienestar!
          </p>
          <a href="/" class="mt-4 inline-block rounded bg-verdeoscuro hover:bg-verdeclaro px-4 py-2 text-white transition-colors">
            Volver al inicio
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>